wikipedia_page.main: Martin Page (born 1 January 1800 at Cambridge; died 28 February 1874 at Cambridge) was an English professional cricketer who played first-class cricket from 1820 to 1834 for Cambridge Town Club, making 13 known appearances in first-class matches.
